WEBVTT

00:00:01.100 --> 00:00:07.099
Now, if we think about Jesus' words in today's text,

00:00:07.099 --> 00:00:10.099
give us today our bread for this day,

00:00:10.099 --> 00:00:14.099
there's really indirect counsel against materialism.

00:00:14.099 --> 00:00:19.100
See, Jesus didn't say to pray for our daily meat

00:00:19.100 --> 00:00:22.100
or some other luxury food item.

00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:27.100
He didn't even say that we should pray for a month's supply of bread.

00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:32.100
Pray for and be content with our bread for the day.

00:00:32.100 --> 00:00:37.100
But as we know, a sizable number of Jehovah's people today

00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:40.100
are being distracted by materialism.

00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:43.100
So, since this is not an imagined,

00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:46.100
but it's a real danger to Jehovah's people,

00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:54.100
let's discuss the theme, beware of the power of materialism.

00:00:54.100 --> 00:00:59.100
I recall the story of a sister and her two sons

00:00:59.100 --> 00:01:04.099
who were exiled to Siberia.

00:01:04.099 --> 00:01:06.099
Now, they were very poor.

00:01:06.099 --> 00:01:09.099
In fact, they were so poor at times

00:01:09.099 --> 00:01:14.099
they had to literally eat the bark off trees to survive.

00:01:14.099 --> 00:01:17.099
But they were happy because they were all in the truth.

00:01:17.099 --> 00:01:21.099
But years passed and the three of them had opportunity

00:01:21.099 --> 00:01:24.099
to immigrate to the United States.

00:01:24.099 --> 00:01:28.099
The two sons got excellent jobs, high paying jobs,

00:01:28.099 --> 00:01:32.099
as machinas, but in their material prosperity,

00:01:32.099 --> 00:01:36.099
both sons fell out of the truth.

00:01:36.099 --> 00:01:38.099
The sister tearfully remarked,

00:01:38.099 --> 00:01:40.099
I would rather be back in Siberia,

00:01:40.099 --> 00:01:43.099
eating the bark off trees to survive,

00:01:43.099 --> 00:01:48.099
but with my two sons still in the truth.

00:01:48.099 --> 00:01:52.099
Well, numerous other experiences could be related

00:01:52.099 --> 00:01:55.099
that illustrate the power of materialism.

00:01:55.099 --> 00:02:00.099
In fact, it may well be that Satan's most effective trap

00:02:00.099 --> 00:02:05.099
against Jehovah's people in these last days is materialism.

00:02:05.099 --> 00:02:07.099
But now you might be thinking,

00:02:07.099 --> 00:02:11.099
well, isn't sexual immorality by far the number one cause

00:02:11.099 --> 00:02:13.099
for disfellowshipping?

00:02:13.099 --> 00:02:15.099
That's true.

00:02:15.099 --> 00:02:18.099
But we don't have figures for ones who fall away to materialism.

00:02:18.099 --> 00:02:20.099
They're not disfellowshipped.

00:02:20.099 --> 00:02:25.099
And furthermore, how many who succumbed as sexual immorality

00:02:25.099 --> 00:02:30.099
were first weakened spiritually by materialism?

00:02:30.099 --> 00:02:33.099
Well, at least we can say that materialism

00:02:33.099 --> 00:02:37.099
is one of Satan's most effective tools

00:02:37.099 --> 00:02:41.099
are traps against Jehovah's people today.

00:02:42.099 --> 00:02:46.099
And no wonder that humans and Satan's world

00:02:46.099 --> 00:02:51.099
are bombarded with so many advertising messages designed

00:02:51.099 --> 00:02:54.099
to make us want things, even if we don't need these things.

00:02:54.099 --> 00:02:57.099
There was an awake magazine a while back

00:02:57.099 --> 00:03:02.099
that discussed how that Americans may be bombarded

00:03:02.099 --> 00:03:07.099
with up to 1,600 advertising messages every day.

00:03:07.099 --> 00:03:09.099
Imagine that.

00:03:09.099 --> 00:03:14.099
And none of us can feel we're immune to this pressure

00:03:14.099 --> 00:03:16.099
that it can't happen to us.

00:03:16.099 --> 00:03:17.099
It can happen to any of us.

00:03:17.099 --> 00:03:22.099
We could slowly gradually begin to desire material things,

00:03:22.099 --> 00:03:25.099
