00:03:46.099 --> 00:03:48.099
to do work on his trailer.

00:03:48.099 --> 00:03:50.099
But then shortly after he bought this drill,

00:03:50.099 --> 00:03:52.099
they came out with a reversible drill.

00:03:52.099 --> 00:03:54.099
And he thought, well, you know, that'd be nice

00:03:54.099 --> 00:03:56.099
to have a reversible drill.

00:03:56.099 --> 00:03:58.099
It would be much easier to extract the drill bit

00:03:58.099 --> 00:04:02.099
out of the hole, so he bought a reversible drill.

00:04:02.099 --> 00:04:05.099
Shortly after that, they came out with a reversible drill

00:04:05.099 --> 00:04:08.099
had a little light on it.

00:04:08.099 --> 00:04:11.099
You pull the trigger, a little light would come on.

00:04:11.099 --> 00:04:13.099
And he thought, you know, that would be really nice.

00:04:13.099 --> 00:04:15.099
My drill doesn't have a little light on it.

00:04:15.099 --> 00:04:18.100
He was about ready to buy this latest model.

00:04:18.100 --> 00:04:20.100
And then he said, wait a minute.

00:04:20.100 --> 00:04:22.100
What am I doing?

00:04:22.100 --> 00:04:27.100
How often am I going to be drilling at night?

00:04:27.100 --> 00:04:33.310
